== Early Life ==
Thomas was raised by his parents, Clair Cahill and James Canterbury, but also his step-mother ,Jessica Morris, and his step father, Wayne Brackley ( her mother became Clair Brackley) , who has 3 children. Early in his life, all seems perfect, nothing bad to say.He became friends with many people but get rifd of them later.

== Studies and love ==
Thomas eventually went to Engineering studies.It is at this period that he met his love, the one he really loved : Evelyn Chaplin.But after finishing his studies,It is in 1980, that he welcomed his first daughter : Leah Canterbury.He applied for higher education, but also as a pool cleaner, to pay off his first loan.After one year, he qui his part time job to be better at school.After finishing his studies, he couldn't find an engineer job and so he worked on many part-time job.He got Samantha in 1984 then he got Chloe in 1986.The same year, he had dark thought and poisoned his wife.Actually, nobody is sure that he killed her but what is sure is that his wife died unexplicably at the tender age of 29 in 1986.He then spent more time with his daughter, until the sad day of 13 april 1988..

== Heroic Death ==
Thomas Canterbury was found dead in a street, stabbed 10 times. Witnesses says that they saw him trying to break a knife battle.His heroic death mades his 3 daughter orphelin at the age of 8, 4 and 2.

His funeral was attended by his father, his mother, his step-father, his step-mother and his 3 daughters.His death is also tragic because his daughter would never have known their parents..